@startuml
title ProspectOS End-to-End Lead Prospecting Flow

actor User
participant "Frontend / UI" as UI
participant "Lead Search API" as SearchApi
participant "Discovery Orchestrator" as Discovery
participant "Google Places" as GooglePlaces
participant "Apify" as Apify
participant "Prospect Enrichment API" as EnrichApi
participant "Internal Website Auditor" as InternalAudit
participant "Google PageSpeed" as PageSpeed
participant "Hunter Domain Search" as Hunter
participant "Outreach Delivery API" as DeliveryApi
participant "Resend" as Resend

User -> UI : Search local businesses\n(e.g. clinics in Orlando)
UI -> SearchApi : POST /api/leads/search
SearchApi -> Discovery : discover(query, sources, limit)

alt Primary source healthy
    Discovery -> GooglePlaces : search businesses
    GooglePlaces --> Discovery : businesses with website/phone/address
else Fallback source selected
    Discovery -> Apify : scrape maps results
    Apify --> Discovery : businesses with website/phone/address
end

Discovery --> SearchApi : lead candidates
SearchApi --> UI : discovered companies

User -> UI : Enrich selected prospect
UI -> EnrichApi : POST /api/prospect/enrich
EnrichApi -> InternalAudit : audit website heuristics
InternalAudit --> EnrichApi : internal score + findings
EnrichApi -> PageSpeed : run technical audit
PageSpeed --> EnrichApi : technical score + findings
EnrichApi -> Hunter : domain search
Hunter --> EnrichApi : contacts by domain
EnrichApi --> UI : audit + contacts + analysis

User -> UI : Send outreach
UI -> DeliveryApi : POST /api/outreach/deliveries
DeliveryApi -> Resend : send email
Resend --> DeliveryApi : delivery id
DeliveryApi --> UI : SENT + delivery id

note over UI,DeliveryApi
Human review can happen before the final send step.
The system automates lookup, qualification, and delivery.
end note

@enduml
